Description: Company Description	ABOUT THE COMPANY Analytics Data Factory s.r.o. has been operating on the Czech market since 2015. As a proud GOLD partner of SAS, we implement products for customers that provide a complete overview of not only business opportunities and project management effectiveness, but also the identification of a wide variety of possible risks. In the end, the basis of every successful business decision is the right data analysis. A RELIABLE SUPPLIER WITH A CLEAR VISION Customer satisfaction is our number one priority and why we strive for the long-term development of the solutions we deliver, including high quality service, which is the key to strengthening and building strong relationships with our clients. We are a young, dynamic company that cares about our people and our company culture. In addition to team building events and other non-work functions, there are many opportunities for professional growth, personal development, continuing education and certifications. We also make sure that we take care of the people and society around us. We support many charitable projects and our employees actively participate in charity events. OUR SERVICES The basis of every successful decision in business is the right data analysis. Thanks to our services, you will always have a complete overview of not only business opportunities and project management effectiveness, but also the identification of a wide variety of possible risks. CRM BY ADF We specialize in the development of CRM systems as a unit. Our operational CRM services focus on the implementation of a simple, accessible and responsive application. The emphasis on optimization creates a clear 360-degree overview for each user or user role and is the key to customer satisfaction. The result of our implementations is a modular application that reflects the real needs of users with respect to a specific business model. FRAUD BY ADF We help you set up and manage fraud detection processes. Our services in the field of fraud detection systems include not only a complete analysis of process settings, but also the subsequent support of their management, including complete management and development of technologies that significantly facilitate the detection of non-standard behavior. We apply our know-how mainly in the banking and insurance industries. OFFICE BY ADF We offer an effective management system for your office. A set of functions and work processes will allow you to efficiently manage your office, your colleagues and effectively report project, work and financial results according to your needs. The complete flexibility of our system will allow you to tailor the system directly to your requirements. SUPPORT BY ADF We provide support for SAS products and solutions. Support by ADF is about an individual approach to the customer supported by the skill of our experts and a wide portfolio of offered services.
Certifications: SAS Certified Advanced Programmer for SAS 9, SAS Certified Base Programmer for SAS 9
Additional Experience: Analytic Modernization, Fraud (Security Intelligence), Risk Management

Name: Arrayworks Inc
Description:
Arrayworks’ Transformation Acceleration Platform (TAP), is a low-code AIoT Application Enablement Platform. TAP’s unique architecture is ideally suited to help enterprises create and operationalize a “Digital Twin” of their organization creating visibility, delivering situational awareness, supporting improved enterprise decisions, assuring compliance with regulations or best practices, minimizing risk and automating complex event orchestration.

SAS and Arrayworks have partnered to deliver a complete AIoT solution. From edge to operations, we enable customers to monitor operations for critical events, notify and orchestrate appropriate AI driven responses and launch processes to track and resolve issues. SAS delivers the Power To Know® and Arrayworks delivers the Power To Do. Together we deliver a complete edge to operations solution that allows organizations to seamlessly model, monitor and manage their entire digital value stream.
Industries: Insurance, Health Care and Life Sciences, Manufacturing, Public Sector/Government
